.TH "MAILSEND\-GO" "1" "June 2026" "mailsend\-go v1.0.12" "User Manual"
.SH Introduction
\c
.UR https://github.com/muquit/mailsend-go
mailsend\-go
.UE \c
\ is a command line tool to send mail via SMTP protocol.
This is the \c
.UR https://golang.org/
golang
.UE \c
\ incarnation of my C version of \c
.UR https://github.com/muquit/mailsend/
mailsend
.UE \c
\&.
However, this version is much simpler and all the heavy lifting is done
by the package \c
.UR https://gopkg.in/gomail.v2
gomail.v2
.UE \c
\ However, this package is not maintained anymore.
Therefore, I forked it to \c
.UR https://github.com/muquit/gomail
gomail
.UE \c
\ (starting from mailsend\-go v1.0.11\-b1 Aug\-24\-2025).
The main purpose of this fork is to add \c
.UR https://developers.google.com/workspace/gmail/imap/xoauth2-protocol
XOAUTH2
.UE \c
\ support (Bug #68) but it also contains a security fix to prevent
STARTTLS downgrade attack.
.PP
If you use \c
.UR https://github.com/muquit/mailsend/
mailsend
.UE \c
\ , please consider using mailsend\-go as no new features will be added
to \c
.UR https://github.com/muquit/mailsend/
mailsend
.UE \c
\&.
.PP
If you have any question, request or suggestion, please enter it in the
\c
.UR https://github.com/muquit/mailsend-go/issues
Issues
.UE \c
\ with appropriate label.
.PP
\f[B]NOTE:\f[R] XOAUTH2 support was added in v1.0.11\-b1 (Released on
Aug\-24\-2025)
.PP
Please look at ChangeLog for what has changed in the current version.
.SH XOAUTH2 support
\c
.UR https://developers.google.com/workspace/gmail/imap/xoauth2-protocol
XOAUTH2
.UE \c
\ support is available in v1.0.11\-b1 (Released on Aug\-24\-2025).
\c
.UR https://github.com/muquit/mailsend-go
mailsend\-go
.UE \c
\ itself does not implement full OAuth2 flow because implementing full
OAuth2 would require managing web browser redirects, secure token
storage across different platforms and maintaing state of token refresh
cycles.
.PP
Therefore, I\(cqve created a companion tool called \c
.UR https://github.com/muquit/oauth-helper
oauth\-helper
.UE \c
\ for token management.
This separation keeps \c
.UR https://github.com/muquit/mailsend-go
mailsend\-go
.UE \c
\ simple and secure while giving you full control over how tokens are
obtained and stored.
For automation, just pipe token from \c
.UR https://github.com/muquit/oauth-helper
oauth\-helper
.UE \c
\ directly into \c
.UR https://github.com/muquit/mailsend-go
mailsend\-go
.UE \c
\&.
.PP
Please visit \c
.UR https://github.com/muquit/oauth-helper
oauth\-helper
.UE \c
\ page for details.
It has examples on how to integrate with \c
.UR https://github.com/muquit/mailsend-go
mailsend\-go
.UE \c
\ and \c
.UR https://developers.google.com/workspace/gmail/imap/xoauth2-protocol
XOAUTH2
.UE \c
\&.
.PP
Please create an \c
.UR https://github.com/muquit/mailsend-go/issues
Issues
.UE \c
\ if you need help or have any questions.
